title: Rent4Wheels
description: A car rental application made in Laravel/PHP using CSS framework bootstrap. The purpose of this project was to provide facility for users to rent a car whenever they want.

title: DSA Project
description: This Project was made to test our Data Structures and Alogorithms logic. We used a data set of FIFA 19, and organized it using Arrays, Linked List, AVL trees and graphs. C++ and Qt was used for this project.

title: Sudoku
description: I created a Sudoku game in my first semester, where user has to complete the 9x9 grid following some rules. This game was created using python and PyQt6.
